@startuml
skinparam Shadowing true
skinparam RoundCorner 5
skinparam MaxMessageSize 250

queue "Kafka\ntopic: patient" as KF #FADBD8

box "analytics-service" #5D6D7E
    participant "KafkaConsumer\n(@KafkaListener)" as Consumer #White
    participant "protobuf-java" as Proto #White
end box

group #LightCyan Обработка события PatientEvent\nKafka topic: patient → analytics-service (groupId: analytics-service)

    KF -> Consumer ++: **[1]** consumeEvent(byte[] event)\n(Spring Kafka delivers message)

    Consumer -> Proto ++: **[2]** PatientEvent.parseFrom(event)

    alt #MistyRose Повреждённые данные / неверный формат
        Proto --[#red]> Consumer: <color:#red>InvalidProtocolBufferException</color>

        Consumer -> Consumer: <color:#red>catch(InvalidProtocolBufferException e)\nlog.error("Error deserializing event {}", e.getMessage())</color>
        note right of Consumer: **Silent Data Loss:**\nАвто-коммит offset выполнен.\nСообщение потеряно безвозвратно\n(DLQ не настроен).
    end

    Proto --> Consumer --: PatientEvent object

    Consumer -> Consumer: **[3]** Извлечение полей:\npatientId, name, email

    Consumer -> Consumer: **[4]** log.info(\n"Received Patient Event:\n[PatientId={},PatientName={},PatientEmail={}]",\npatientId, name, email)

    Consumer --> KF --: **[5]** Авто-коммит offset\n(Spring Kafka auto-commit)

end
@enduml
